{
  "stem": "10181.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But even so, they claim that they had to do it because the Germans made them do it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's neither here nor there anyways.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's not part of my story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Vught was-- men were put in one side, and women were put in another part of the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was together with my cousin but not with my sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister was together with my aunt and my other cousin for a while.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my uncle was in a different part, OK?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened in Vught was it was divided according to whatever you were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you were Jewish, you had a yellow star.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were not only Jews there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were, for instance, if you were a Communist, and you were caught-- supposedly were a Communist-- you had a red triangle on you-- on your suit, or some of them wore the striped suits already.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in Vught, mostly they didn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Usually you wore your own clothes, whatever you had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then if you were supposedly a black marketeer, you had a-- a black little triangle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then if you were somebody they didn't like, or they called them homosexual, but they necessarily-- weren't necessarily homosexual, but they made them put a pink triangle on, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and there were not only Jews there, there were other people there too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And every morning, there was roll call, but you had to be there, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were people trying-- there, people tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Not the Jews mainly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think mainly they were the non-Jews, the-- the people that would work in the underground what got caught and-- and they had connections.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
